{"tid":826118,"cid":13,"subCid":0,"title":"消委會報告：小米空氣淨化機勝dyson","createTime":"2018-09-18T04:20:17.000Z","updateTime":"2018-09-18T04:23:10.000Z","uid":45582,"like":4,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"ee6570a7b1ccbb3efbdd2b4b541d56f5267fa82a","tid":826118,"uid":45582,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-18T04:20:17.000Z","msg":"完全估唔到dyson得分低過小米。<br />\n<br />\n空氣質素問題愈來愈受關注，不少市民會選購空氣淨化機來改善家居空氣質素。消費者委員會測試了市面上12款空氣淨化機，發現樣本去除污染物的速度極為懸殊。去除香煙煙霧、麈埃和花粉速度可相差約2倍，而且部分聲稱適用面積較大的樣本，其除污染物的速度，反不及聲稱適用面積較小的樣本。&nbsp;<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n至於除甲醛的速度最多相差更達26倍，表現最好的為「飛利浦」AC3259/31 ，售價4988港元，潔淨空氣量(CADR)立方呎/分鐘139.9，而「法國特福」PU4065的CADR只有5.1，其售價為2698港元。&nbsp;<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n價錢愈貴的淨化機，又是否一定愈好呢？測試樣本中，價格最低的「小米」空氣淨化器2s(AC-M4-AA)(售價約1099港元)和價格最高的樣本「Blueair」 Classic 405 (SmokeStop)(售價約7080港元)，後者貴超過5倍。前者取得4分總評，後者僅得3.5分，值得注重性價比的消費者留意。&nbsp;<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n「小米」空氣淨化器2s(AC-M4-AA)的空氣淨化表現有3.5分，亦勝過「Dyson」兩款售價俱為約5480港元的二合一空氣淨化風扇，型號分別為Pure Cool TP04(空氣淨化表現3分)、Pure Cool Link TP03(空氣淨化表現2.5分)。&nbsp;<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20180918/bkn-20180918100026013-0918_00822_001.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fnews%2F20180918%2Fbkn-20180918100026013-0918_00822_001.html&d=T59rwxhmKKKIcI%2B98AzLDKMP9SZiTpIcsXSGftWU1%2BE%3D&h=1768e9fd\" target=\"_blank\">http://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20180918/bkn-20180918100026013-0918_00822_001.html</a>"},{"pid":"4620418b33665df902b72b884c4b4c97ec1903c5","tid":826118,"uid":68728,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-18T04:21:41.000Z","msg":"消委會已經赤化？"},{"pid":"6d2a7a4e29dd9d39c1b6d3ce51f11f9ea4472ff2","tid":826118,"uid":39780,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-18T04:21:54.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/09/18/122151_b6548585ddff59d22c39408cba8e280f.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F09%2F18%2F122151_b6548585ddff59d22c39408cba8e280f.gif&h=c240a2c2&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"bbd4f9c49d112389db2c28aa20e011c3a8dece9f","tid":826118,"uid":12757,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"4620418b33665df902b72b884c4b4c97ec1903c5","tid":826118,"uid":68728,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-18T04:21:41.000Z","msg":"消委會已經赤化？"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-18T04:23:10.000Z","msg":"你依家先知？"}]}